      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "1t was reported today that the\nAmerican Federation of Labor, act\ning on advises from Organizer G..\no. Young. would leave the local\nfederal unions to settle their diff\nferences and amalgamate If they\ncan, and If they cannot to permit\nthem to get along in the future as\nthey have in the past.\n\n\nAn effort is being made by local\nmen to bring the two unions to-\ngether. In case these efforts are\nnot successful it Is likely that there\nwill be no further action, as Mr..\nYoung was given to understand\nwhile here that arbitrary action on\nthe part of the federation was very\nlikely to raise a row that would be\nheard by Gompers."
    }
  ]
